  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">LSETF- LoftyInc Digital Literacy Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support efforts aimed at helping poor households (especially female-headed household as they are often the most disadvantaged) connect to the economic opportunities created by growth. It includes both efforts to enhance the current income-earning prospects of poor households, as well as efforts to ensure that they can accumulate and protect productive assets.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support the creation, improvement and sustainability of physical infrastructure, and related services, in both urban and rural areas, to enhance the economic environment and improve economic productivity, including for women. The main infrastructures include energy, including electric power transmission lines and distribution networks, oil/gas terminals, refineries, storage facilities and pipelines; telecom and ICT; and transport, including roads, airports, railways, and ports.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This award strives to generate rapid, sustained, and broad-based economic growth. More specifically, this includes a Loftyinc Allied partners Limited is proposing to deliver digital skills training unemployed Lagos state residents by leveraging her partners across the various spectrum of services required to deliver the program outcome . The company plans to use its strategic partnerships with Microsoft, VMWare and IBM to deliver digital skills training in the following areas: Cloud computing, virtualization, cybersecurity, robotics, coding and blockchain technology. Loftyinc Allied Partners Limited intends to adopt a three-pronged approach for all beneficiaries: Training, job placement and entrepreneurship support. The company plans to have the training in steams. Three streams per year; Fifty students per stream; twelve weeks per stream..</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To generate rapid, sustained, and broad-based economic growth.</narrative>
  </description>
